casebody.data:
Alicia M. Cavanagh v. Lawrence Cavanagh, Executor (Estate of Alicia L. Cavanagh), et al. (9856)

Daly, Foti and Schaller, Js.

Argued November 5 decision released December 1, 1992 Joseph P. Secola filed a brief for the appellant (plaintiff). David D. Legere, with whom, on the brief, were Shelley R. Halber, Robert P. Dolian and William H. Narwold, for the appellees (defendants). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
